<item>
            <title>[SPR-12350] Allow for using the response encoding when escaping HTML characters</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-12350</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Once &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-9293&quot; title=&quot;Greek characters and htmlEscape()&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SPR-9293&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SPR-9293&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; is fixed, &lt;tt&gt;HtmlUtils.htmlescape&lt;/tt&gt; calls should be updated throughout the framework (e.g. JSP tags, etc) to provide the current response encoding to the method in order to handle HTML escaping properly.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
            <key id="60265">SPR-12350</key>
            <summary>Allow for using the response encoding when escaping HTML characters</summary>
